			"body": {
				"mimeType": "application/json",
				"text": "{\n  \"parts\": [\n    {\n      \"partNumber\": 1,\n      \"userResponse\": \"I come from Verona, Italy. It's a beautiful historic city famous for Romeo and Juliet. I've lived there my whole life and love the architecture and cultural events.\",\n      \"timeSpent\": 120\n    },\n    {\n      \"partNumber\": 2,\n      \"userResponse\": \"One memorable event in my life was graduating from university last year. It happened in June at our campus auditorium. My whole family was there to support me. This event was so memorable because it represented years of hard work paying off. I felt incredibly proud and relieved when I walked across that stage. It marked the beginning of my professional career and made my parents extremely happy.\",\n      \"timeSpent\": 180\n    },\n    {\n      \"partNumber\": 3,\n      \"userResponse\": \"Technology has significantly changed communication compared to the past. In the past, people relied on letters and face-to-face meetings, which were slower but perhaps more meaningful. Today, we have instant messaging, video calls, and social media that allow immediate global communication. While this has made us more connected globally, I think it has also made communication more superficial in some ways. People often prefer texting over phone calls, which can lead to misunderstandings. However, the benefits are enormous - we can maintain relationships across distances and access information instantly.\",\n      \"timeSpent\": 200\n    }\n  ]\n}"
			},
